[log] bash[68] stdout - Tab detection and replacement: Identify tabs in indentation and replace them with spaces.
[log] bash[68] stdout - Indentation size standardization: Adjust the indentation size according to the configuration (1, 2, 3, 4 spaces).
[log] bash[68] stdout - Multi-line string protection: Avoid modifying tabs within multi-line strings.
[log] bash[68] stdout - Docstring processing: Correctly handle indentation in docstrings.
