[log] bash[68] stdout **Core Algorithm**:
[log] bash[68] stdout - Whitespace processing inside parentheses: Remove extra spaces inside parentheses.
[log] bash[68] stdout - Spaces around operators: Add or remove spaces before and after operators.
[log] bash[68] stdout - Spaces after commas: Add spaces after commas.
[log] bash[68] stdout - Trailing whitespace cleaning: Remove extra whitespace at the end of lines.
